            {
              "id": "SimplifiedTernary",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "This conditional expression can be simplified with || or &&"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "\n\nReports ternary expression with the form `condition ? literalBoolean : foo`\nor `condition ? foo : literalBoolean`.\n\nThese expressions can be simplified as follows:\n* `condition ? true : expr` simplifies to `condition || expr`\n* `condition ? false : expr` simplifies to `!condition && expr`\n* `condition ? expr : true` simplifies to `!condition || expr`\n* `condition ? expr : false` simplifies to `condition && expr`\n\n        "
              },
              "helpUri": "https://docs.pmd-code.org/snapshot/pmd_rules_java_design.html#simplifiedternary",
              "help": {
                "text": "\n\nReports ternary expression with the form `condition ? literalBoolean : foo`\nor `condition ? foo : literalBoolean`.\n\nThese expressions can be simplified as follows:\n* `condition ? true : expr` simplifies to `condition || expr`\n* `condition ? false : expr` simplifies to `!condition && expr`\n* `condition ? expr : true` simplifies to `!condition || expr`\n* `condition ? expr : false` simplifies to `condition && expr`\n\n        "
              },
              "properties": {
                "ruleset": "Design",
                "priority": 3,
                "tags": [
                  "Design"
                ]
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
